  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK296">
<l>poyyāmai yaṉṉa pukaḻillai poyyāmai</l>
<l>yellā vaṟamun tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no praise like the praise of never uttering a falsehood: without causing any suffering, it will lead to every virtue.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
